":31814,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Zaynab: The generosity of the Prophet\u2019s wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Some of the wives of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cWhich of us will be the quickest to meet you?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe one with the longest hand.\u201d They measured their hands with sticks and Sawdah had the longest of them,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/18\/prophet-threaten-spanking\/","url_meta":{"origin":31814,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Discipline: The Prophet threatens spanking, but fears Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was in her house when he called for her servant girl. When the servant was delayed, the displeasure of the Prophet could be seen on his face. Umm Salamah arose and looked through the curtain to see the girl\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14341,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/righteous-evil-dominates-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":31814,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Magog: Righteous will perish if evil dominates","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zaynab bint Jahsh reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came to me while he was frightened and he said, \u201cThere is no God but Allah! Woe to the Arabs from an evil drawing near! An opening has been made today in the barrier of Gog and Magog\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31761,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/qiraat-harf-harf\/","url_meta":{"origin":31814,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: The Prophet recited Quran clearly, word by word","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ya\u2019la ibn Mamlak reported: He asked Umm Salamah, the wife of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, about his recitation and his prayer. Umm Salamah said, \u201cNot as you can pray. The Prophet would pray, then sleep for the amount he prayed. Then he would pray the amount\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/31\/magic-spells-amulets-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":31814,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Spells: Amulets and charms are forbidden medicine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, magic spells, amulets, and charms are acts of idolatry.\u201d Abdullah\u2019s wife, Zaynab, said, \u201cWhy do you say this? By Allah, I would go to